X:12
T:XII - Accent Combinations
C:Rodriguez Do Campo Method (2020)
M:4/4
L:1/8
Q:1/4=80
K:C
%%text Same scale, accents shift position each pass.
%%text Pass 1: accent on beat 1. Pass 2: accent on beat 2. Etc.
%%text Combine different fingerings per hand: e.g. RH 4-3-2-1, LH 2-4-3-1
!accent!CDEF GABC|!accent!defg abc'd'|c'8|
C!accent!DEF GABc|d!accent!efg abc'd'|c'8|
CD!accent!EF GABc|de!accent!fg abc'd'|c'8|
CDE!accent!F GABc|def!accent!g abc'd'|c'8|]
